items.name: Bundle for 1 Bae
items.description: Briyani + Drink to complete the meal!

items.name: Hyderabadi Biryani (Lamb Biryani)
items.description: Yogurt marinated lamb simmered with long grain basmati rice, fresh herbs and frangrant spices till tender. Comes with mixed raita.

items.name: Lucknowi Biryani (Chicken Biryani)
items.description: Delicious savoury rice dish loaded with juicy marinated chicken, caramelized onions and flavorful saffron rice. Comes with mixed raita.

items.name: Kolkata Biryani
items.description: Basmati rice, juicy marinated chicken, potatoes and an egg cooked in dum style for an enjoyable feast. Comes with mixed raita.

items.name: Machhli Tikka Biryani (Fish Biryani)
items.description: Tandoor baked fish simmered with freshly ground herbs, long grain basmati rice and spices. Comes with mixed raita.

items.name: Lamb Shank Biryani
items.description: An Attas biryani specialty for those who are crazy about succulent lamb shanks with flavourful biryani rice. Comes with mixed raita.

items.name: Subz Biryani (Vegetable Biryani)
items.description: Basmati rice cooked with fresh vegetables, herbs and freshly ground spices. Comes with mixed raita.

items.name: Egg Biryani (comes with 2 Eggs)
items.description: Fragrant basmati rice cooked with fresh aromatic spices, herbs and two boiled eggs. Comes with mixed raita.

items.name: Mango Lassi (cup)
items.description: Cold Indian yogurt drink blended with spices & mango

items.name: Sweet Lassi (cup)
items.description: Cold Indian yogurt drink blended with spices & sugar

items.name: Salt Lassi (cup)
items.description: Cold Indian yogurt drink blended with spices & a hint of salt

items.name: Soft Drink (can)
items.description: Choose from a selection of coke, sprite, & 100 plus
